flowchart LR
    UserA([User A])
    UserB([User B])
    ChatSvrA[Chat Server A<br/>sticky WS]
    ChatSvrB[Chat Server B<br/>sticky WS]
    Bus[(Message Bus<br/>partitioned event stream)]
    Persist[Persist Service]
    PushSvc[Push Notif Service]
    History[(Wide-Column<br/>Message Store)]
    Registry[(Session Registry<br/>in-memory cache)]

    UserA <-->|WebSocket| ChatSvrA
    UserB <-->|WebSocket| ChatSvrB
    ChatSvrA --> Persist
    ChatSvrB --> Persist
    Persist --> History
    ChatSvrA -.->|publish| Bus
    Bus -.->|subscribe| ChatSvrB
    ChatSvrA -->|lookup| Registry
    Persist -.->|if offline| PushSvc

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class UserA,UserB external
    class ChatSvrA,ChatSvrB,Persist,PushSvc service
    class Bus,History,Registry store
